        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''There has never been a military commander in history who wouldn't like to have more of something or other. That characterizes all of us here. The fact is, frankly, that we have all that our country is going to provide us in terms of combat forces -- that is really it, right now.''</p>
        <p>GEN. DAVID H. PETRAEUS, the top American commander in Iraq. [10]</p>
      </block>
